snippet.title: [Solo Leveling:ARISE] 1st Main Promo Video
snippet.description:
A World-changing "Level Up'' Begins!
A first look at [Solo Leveling:ARISE]!

Solo Leveling, the popular webtoon with 14.2 billion global views: reborn as an action RPG!

Want to learn more? Then keep a lookout for updates on our official channel: 

■ Official Website
https://sololeveling.netmarble.com

■ Official Twitter
https://twitter.com/Sololv_ARISE_GL

■ Official Facebook
https://www.facebook.com/SoloLevelingARISE.EN
https://www.facebook.com/SoloLevelingARISE.TH

■ Official Instagram 
https://www.instagram.com/sololeveling.arise

#SoloLevelingARISE #SoloLeveling #ARISE #OnlyILevelUp #SungJinwoo #netmarble
